"{\"uid\": \"malaya.com.ph-weekly-features-travel-tourism-paris-hotels-triple-prices-for-olympics-opening-night\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 6, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- Paris hotels are tripling their prices to more than 1,000 euros ($1,092) on average for the opening night of the 2024 Olympic games, according to a consumer organization study.\", \"from\": 7, \"to\": 185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999997927998593, \"rank\": 2.0720056221066098e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UFC-Que Choisir said a late-December poll of 80 three- and four-star hotels showed that on the night of July 26, the day of the Olympics' opening ceremony on the banks of the Seine River, a double room will cost 1,033 euros ($1,128) on average, compared to 317 euros two weeks earlier on the night of July 12.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC-Que_Choisir\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UFC-Que Choisir\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC-Que_Choisir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC-Que_Choisir\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also said 50% of these hotels reported being already fully booked that night, while 30% required a minimum booking of at least two nights and some as many as five nights.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The average required minimum stay was 3.4 days, for an average cost of 867 euros per night, UFC added.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 0.997797739572031, \"rank\": 0.0022069365483879887, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympic room rates!\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris hotels are not holding back, their room rates are on fire,\\\" UFC said.\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999997927998593, \"rank\": 2.0720056221066098e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 0.997797739572031, \"rank\": 0.0022069365483879887, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share post:  Malaya Business Insight comes to you in a very readable package: A fusion of in-depth news, excellent news analyses, the credible prognosis of events, powerful commentaries and balanced updates on what is happening and about to happen in corporate board rooms, in the diverse business and industry sectors, in Philippine regional and global politics and in the exciting world of sports, arts, entertainment, and lifestyle.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 Malaya Business Insight.All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Developed byNeitiviti Studios\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}]}"